	<title>Instructions for Sign-up</title>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="container-fluid">
		<div style="background-color:#ff9933; padding:5px;"><h1 align="center"><strong>Instructions for Sign-up</strong></h1></div>
		
		<ul>
			<li><h3><i>Your Name</i></h3>
				<ul>
					<li>At least 4 characters and at most 40 characters.</li>
					<li>At least 2 words and differentiated by space/s</li>
					<li>Must not use any spaces at the beginning or end of your Name.</li>
					<li>Ex. "abc def"</li>
				</ul>
			</li>
			<li><h3><i>User Name</i></h3>
				<ul>
					<li>At least 4 characters and at most 20 characters.</li>
					<li>Must not use any spaces in User Name.</li>
					<li>Ex. "abcxyz"</li>
				</ul>
			</li>
  			<li><h3><i>Password</i></h3>
				<ul>
					<li>At least 8 characters and at most 40 characters.</li>
					<li>Must not use any spaces in Password.</li>
					<li>Must not same as User Name.</li>
					<li>Must contain a 'upper-case', a 'lower-case' and a 'number'.</li>
					<li>Ex. "pQr9t"</li>
				</ul>
			</li>
			<li><h3><i>Confirm Password</i></h3>
				<ul>
					<li>Confirm Password must be same as Password that you have entered.</li>
				</ul>
			</li>
		</ul>
		
	</div>
</body>
</html>